# Naming Conventions

## Interfaces
- Prefix with `I` + PascalCase
- Examples: `IShortenService`, `ICacheService`, `IRabbitMqBus`

## Implementations
- Descriptive name + `Service` suffix
- Examples: `Base62ShortenService`, `MemoryCacheService`

## Entities
- PascalCase, singular nouns
- Examples: `ShortenLink`, `BaseEntity<T>`

## Methods
- PascalCase, async methods end with `Async`
- Examples: `ShortenUrlAsync()`, `GetShortenPureValueAsync()`

## Private Fields
- `_` prefix + camelCase
- Examples: `_context`, `_hostDomain`, `_messageBus`

## Constants
- PascalCase
- Examples: `UpdateShortenPathQueue`

## Queue Names (RabbitMQ)
- kebab-case, descriptive
- Examples: `shorten-link.update`
